description:
STAR WARS VINTAGE ENCYCLOPEDIA ON A PC CD-ROM

THE ORIGINAL DISK CREATED BY BRANCOBADGER

This disk has been created by brancobadger and all the items used are 100% Original Vintage Star Wars.

Why pay for replacement decals / stickers, instructions and cardbacks when you can have nearly all of them on this disk and create them yourself, saving you Ã‚Â£Ã‚Â£Ã‚Â£Ã‚Â£Ã‚Â£'s.

It contains A New Hope, The Empire Strikes Back, Return of the Jedi, The Power of the Force, Ewoks and Droids.

The disk contains images that could be used to create replacement decals / stickers, instructions and cardbacks for almost all vintage figures and nearly all Vehicles and Playsets.  Plus Catalogues for all 3 films, Early Bird and Bounty Hunter Log.

The images are the exact size when printed,  approx. 96 dpi.

The disk also contains pictures of the vehicles and playsets for identification purposes.
